title: Top 30 Country Oct 13, 2015
description:
4 new songs appear on our Top 30 chart this week, which means 4 had to disappear.  Lady Antebellum didnâ€™t score big with Long Stretch of Love as it falls off the chart, as does Chris Janson (who did hit #1 with Buy Me A Boat), Jake Owen and Thomas Rhett.  Do not feel bad for Thomas however, as his single Die A Happy Man debuts at #30 for the week.  Here are the U.S. Top 30 Country singles as ranked by Mediabase for the week of October 13, 2015 in mp3 320 Constant Bit Rate with the run time.
